# Global Working Defaults

Always respond in zh-TW (繁體中文). Use zh-TW for all explanations, comments, and communications. Technical terms and code identifiers remain in their original form.

ECC (everything-claude-code) is installed at `~/.claude/plugins/everything-claude-code/`.
Rules, agents, commands, hooks, and skills are managed by ECC.

Refer to ECC's AGENTS.md for core principles: Agent-First, TDD, Security-First, Immutability, Research-First.

Use `/ecc-profile` to switch hook enforcement level within a session (off/minimal/standard/strict).

## gstack

- gstack is installed at `~/.claude/skills/gstack`
- Prefer gstack `/browse` for browser-driven QA
- Do not use `mcp__claude-in-chrome__*` tools
- Available gstack skills: /office-hours, /plan-ceo-review, /plan-eng-review, /plan-design-review, /design-consultation, /review, /ship, /browse, /qa, /qa-only, /design-review, /setup-browser-cookies, /retro, /investigate, /document-release, /codex, /careful, /freeze, /guard, /unfreeze, /gstack-upgrade
- Use gstack `/codex` as the primary Codex wrapper
